      <h1>I Told You So</h1>
      <p class="lead">I Told You So helps you record predictions, settle outcomes, and share receipts. The app is designed to keep your prediction history on your device.</p>
      <p class="label">Last updated: April 27, 2026</p>
    </section>

    <section class="work">
      <div class="section-head">
        <p class="sub-header">Data Collection</p>
        <h2>No personal data is collected by the developer.</h2>
      </div>
      <p>I Told You So does not require an account and does not send your prediction content to a developer-operated server.</p>
      <p>The app may store predictions, history, verdicts, and generated receipt content locally on your device so the app can function.</p>
      <p>If you choose to share a receipt or screenshot, that content is shared only through the iOS share sheet and only with the people or services you select.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="work">
      <div class="section-head">
        <p class="sub-header">Third Parties</p>
        <h2>Apple system services may apply.</h2>
      </div>
      <p>Apple may process limited technical information as part of iOS, App Store, crash diagnostics, or other system services, depending on your device settings. This is governed by Apple’s own policies.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="work">
      <div class="section-head">
        <p class="sub-header">Contact</p>
        <h2>Questions?</h2>
      </div>
      <p>Contact the developer at <a href="/contact">hannesnagel.com/contact</a>.</p>
    </section>
